title: Muhurat of ‘Maee Ke Acharwa Babuji Ke Dular’ held in Mumbai
text:
The muhurat of Maee Ke Acharwa Babuji Ke Dular starring Vinod Tiwari and Kunal Singh was recently held in Mumbai.
The film will mark the debut of Bablu Master. The female lead of the film is Neha. Maee Ke Acharwa Babuji Ke Dular will also feature ace actors like Baleshwar Singh, Dharmendra Singh and CP Bhatt in important roles.
Produced by Kamini Ben Kannu Bhai Patel under the banner of Brajraj Films, the film will be directed by Shyamcharan Yadav. Ashok Lal Dehati has worked on the film's story and screenplay. The music for the film will be composed by Ashok Sinha.
Source: Bhojpurimedia.com
